					bindings = <
// ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷   ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷
                &kp N1      &kp N2      &kp N3      &kp N4      &kp N5          &kp N6      &kp N7      &kp N8      &kp N9      &kp N0
                &kp ESC     &none       &none       &none       &none           &none       &none       &none       &none       &kp MINUS
    &kp LALT    &kp TAB     &kp GRAVE   &none       &none       &none           &none       &none       &kp EQUAL   &kp RBKT    &kp LBKT    &kp BSLH
                                        &none       &none       &kp LSHFT       &none       &none       &none
